OL,3,CParents' campaign for safer nurseries
OL,4,Cafter baby's death one step closer
OL,6,FThe parents of a nine-month-old girl,
OL,7,Fwho was killed by her nursery worker,
OL,8,Fsay they "welcome" the government's
OL,9,Fengagement in their recently launched
OL,10,Fcampaign calling for change in early
OL,11,Fyears settings.
OL,13,FThe minister for Early Education
OL,14,FStephen Morgan says he is reviewing
OL,15,Fcalls from Genevieve 'Gigi' Meehan's
OL,16,Fparents for CCTV to be made mandatory
OL,17,Fin early years settings. He is also
OL,18,Fconsidering if changes need to be made
OL,19,Fto safe sleep requirements.
