OL,3,CParents' campaign for safer nurseries
OL,4,Cafter baby's death one step closer
OL,6,FGenevieve died after she was tightly
OL,7,Fswaddled and strapped face down on a
OL,8,Fbeanbag for more than an hour and a
OL,9,Fhalf at the now closed Tiny Toes
OL,10,Fnursery in Cheadle Hulme, Stockport,
OL,11,Fin May 2022.
OL,13,FKate Roughley, who was the nursery's
OL,14,Fdeputy manager at the time of baby
OL,15,FGenevieve's death, was found guilty of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter and jailed for 14 years
OL,17,Fin May 2024.
