OL,3,CParents' campaign for safer nurseries
OL,4,Cafter baby's death one step closer
OL,6,FHe announced that the government "will
OL,7,Fcontinue to consider" their
OL,8,Fsuggestions to make early years
OL,9,Fsettings safer, including working with
OL,10,FOfsted to "look at the use of CCTV" in
OL,11,Fnurseries, pre-schools and playgroups.
OL,13,FHe added that government officials
OL,14,Fwill be meeting with Jenny Ward, CEO
OL,15,Fof the Lullaby Trust, and NHS
OL,16,Fcolleagues to discuss if changes need
OL,17,Fto be made around safer sleep
OL,18,Frequirements in the Early Years
OL,19,FFoundation Stage (EYFS) statutory
OL,20,Fframework.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
