OL,3,CParents' campaign for safer nurseries
OL,4,Cafter baby's death one step closer
OL,6,FMr Morgan also said, as of next April,
OL,7,FOfsted will inspect all new providers
OL,8,Fon the early years register "within 18
OL,9,Fmonths of opening" and move towards
OL,10,Finspections every four years, instead
OL,11,Fof every six.
OL,13,FWhat are the three main points of the
OL,14,Fcampaign?
OL,16,FUse of CCTV
OL,18,FOfsted inspection process
