OL,3,CParents' campaign for safer nurseries
OL,4,Cafter baby's death one step closer
OL,6,FIn response to the latest update,
OL,7,FGenevieve's parents, Katie Wheeler and
OL,8,FJohn Meehan said:
OL,10,F"We welcome the government's
OL,11,Fengagement with us and the campaign.
OL,13,F"Whilst progress has been made, there
OL,14,Fis significant work to be done and we
OL,15,Flook forward to working with the
OL,16,Fgovernment to achieve the campaign's
OL,17,Fobjectives."
OL,19,FKatie and John calling for people to
OL,20,Fwrite to their local MP to support
OL,21,Ftheir campaign.
